Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:57.16,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,{Start episode 5 lines}You can solve the mystery, right?{Flashback lines match Golden_Wind_05_BD_Release.ass}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:58.67,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:05:59.54,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.00,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:08.89,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,G-Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:11.18,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Giorno is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:17.69,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Giorno Giovanna... \N You're one crazy son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.56,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,All this just to prove yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:25.03,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,What the hell is wrong with you? {End episode 5 lines}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:28.03,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:29.99,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Th-This Stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:32.58,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Defend yourself with Gold Experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:36.45,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:39.67,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Giorno... Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:42.42,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Stay off that part of the deck, Buccellati.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:44.46,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Seriously, stay way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:48.80,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I still don't see Giorno Giovanna as one of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:54.93,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,...but he seemed damned sure \N you wouldn't abandon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:57.48,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,He's done some pretty crazy shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.94,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Giorno Giovanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:03.19,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,What was your plan \N if that stunt had killed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:07.44,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I'll say it again, Buccellati: \N Stay off that part of the deck. {Lower-cased "stay" since, as I have it, a clause following a semicolon should be lower-cased. I think it can be kept upper-cased if you use a colon instead. - Toa}{I'm more in favor of a period or a colon here. -JMFW}{Agreed, changed to colon -Gyro}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:14.24,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Th-The fly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:16.24,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Narancia's shoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:18.91,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Giorno's power is still active.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:20.50,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Could this mean he's alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:21.83,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,They're here, Buccellati!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:23.88,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Narancia and the enemy \N are below deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.84,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Sticky Fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:36.68,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Narancia, Fugo, Mista, \N and Giorno aren't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:38.98,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,They're somewhere below the fly, you think? {Stylistically, I'm not too sure about dropping the verb. - Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:41.27,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,It's just like Giorno said...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:46.82,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,The enemy isn't just staying hidden and \N attacking us from inside a locker or behind an object...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:49.28,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Hey! The fly's coming back around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:51.57,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.11,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Where is it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:56.53,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Where is the enemy hiding, \N and how are they doing it? {WHO IS YOUR DADDY AND WHAT DOES HE DO?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:59.37,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,As for how the enemy's ability works... {It just works. -J}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:04.58,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I hate to admit it, \N but it looks like Giorno was on to something. {the space stays -- "onto" is generally reserved for movement/location -JMFW}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:06.79,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I'll use my Stand to solve the mystery! {:O}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:10.09,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,But... This spot is dangerous, Buccellati!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:21.14,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Moody Blues!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.61,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Will Narancia from \N five minutes ago work?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:30.57,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Yeah. Should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:39.99,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Is the fly all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.46,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,It's headed toward the bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:45.04,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Now's our chance. Act fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:45.92,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,On it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.81,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,What's that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:01.35,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Headphones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:05.27,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Five minutes ago, \N Narancia was listening to music on his boombox.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:08.94,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,{Start episode 5 lines}Huh? What's wrong with this thing?\NIt just died on me!{Flashback lines match Golden_Wind_05_BD_Release.ass}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.61,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why'd the music stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:12.23,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,{\an8}I just bought it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:15.32,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dammit! \N He's got balls to sell me this piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:18.28,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,{\an8}That geezer from the electronics store \N is gonna pay for this!{End episode 5 lines}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:11.11,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:14.03,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Narancia was attacked a bit after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.32,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I'll fast forward{ to it}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:27.54,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,{Start episode 5 lines}His ten billion belongs to us now!{Flashback lines match Golden_Wind_05_BD_Release.ass}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:30.71,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,With that kind of money, \N the position of capo will be ours for the taking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:32.13,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,A-Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.17,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,{\an8}Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:36.76,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,{\an8}Where in Capri did you \N hide all that treasure, Buccellati?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:38.09,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,{\an8}I can't say just yet. {End episode 5 lines}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:34.26,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I can hear myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:38.09,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Narancia was attacked \N right after this conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:42.06,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Hopefully we'll get a good view \N of how he was attacked, Abbacchio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:45.35,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,My Stand's replay captures events perfectly. {cyberpunk 2001}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:49.06,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,We'll know everything from \N how much Narancia was sweating{:D}, down to his pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:51.82,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,It will follow him wherever he went!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:53.28,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,It's about to start...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:57.49,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Let's get behind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:58.61,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Here comes the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:02.70,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,L-Look! It's just like Giorno's wound!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.20,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:08.83,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,H-He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:15.30,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,He's deflating like a punctured balloon!
Comment: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:23.06,Main,,0,0,0,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:34.23,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,He's deflating from \N the air leaking out of his wound. {but he doesn't go PBBBBBBBBBBBBBBBBT, 0/10 deflation}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:37.78,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,At least we have \N the enemy's ability figured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:40.45,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,He's being sucked in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:42.28,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Pause it, Abbacchio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:51.13,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,So that's it. \N He's inside the pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:53.59,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Here's the answer to our mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:57.92,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,His nails, flesh, and bones \N feel like a floppy condom. {Narancia condom! Narancia condom! Narancia condom! -J}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:11:00.47,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,His shoe and belt buckle, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:02.64,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,At least he still has a pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:05.76,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Just like Giorno said, he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:08.14,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I finally get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:14.23,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,The enemy used his ability on himself, \N allowing him to hide somewhere in the pipes or floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:18.28,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,...as well as drag Mista, \N Fugo, and Giorno along for the ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:22.03,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,That explains why Giorno's fly \N can detect the general area they're in...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:25.66,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,...but can't pinpoint their exact location.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:28.79,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Glad we got his ability nailed down{figured out}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:30.87,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Now we just gotta make pursuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:34.00,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,...find and save Narancia and the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.17,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,...then beat this asshole up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:39.13,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I'm gonna resume Moody Blues' replay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:44.18,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Pursuit? \N Wait a second, Abbacchio!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:47.47,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,You can't fight back or defend yourself \N while replaying something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:49.68,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Entering the pipe is too risky!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:54.36,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I know right where Moody Blues is going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:58.53,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,When this asshole gets close, \N unzip the floor and get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:02.57,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,We can't beat him \N unless we pursue, Buccellati!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:09.91,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,It went left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:11.41,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,That's where he got Mista.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:15.04,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Moody Blues just went \N beneath the life preserver.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:19.55,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,It's headed toward the cabin \N where Fugo and Giorno were taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:23.68,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,So the enemy is moving around \N with Narancia and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:26.26,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,It's starting to slow down...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:28.43,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,That's where the asshole was hiding earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:30.77,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Inside that bollard! {.ura bollard}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:33.44,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,The enemy is right there below deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:36.73,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,He's coming after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:39.40,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if he realized \N we figured out his ability, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.28,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,This one's got balls! {:GOOD:}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:43.74,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,The pipe! \N Unzip it and pull them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:45.70,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Sticky Fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:49.95,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Th-They're not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:52.12,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Where's the enemy, Abbacchio?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:55.42,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Where's your Moody Blues?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:57.08,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Right there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:13:00.63,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,It's my Stand. \N I can tell where it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:01.80,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,It's right around there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:03.09,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Right around where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:04.97,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,It's right where you just unzipped!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:07.93,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I know my Moody Blues is there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:16.35,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:17.60,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:21.86,Thoughts,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Impossible... I know for sure it's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:24.82,Thoughts,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Is there still some mystery \N we haven't solved{here}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:26.20,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:28.03,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,End the replay \N and recall your Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:30.03,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I already did!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:31.66,Thoughts,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Something's wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:35.08,Thoughts,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,What is this wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:38.42,Thoughts,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Where the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:44.17,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Did you hear that, Buccellati?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:46.18,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,That's the sound of a pipe wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:50.35,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,We can't see it, \N but Moody Blues is definitely right below us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:51.89,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Trapped inside the pipe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:52.47,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,{\an8}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:54.81,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,{\an8}The enemy is right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:57.90,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's getting closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.52,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,{\an8}We need to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:56.02,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,The pipe is wide open,\N but somehow it's trapped inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:58.65,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Does that mean it's right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:01.86,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Run?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:07.99,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,That smartass, Giorno Giovanna, \N asked me to solve this mystery. {I don't think the delivery justifies the unnecessary commas, but YMMV. - Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:10.07,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,He's a snot-nosed brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:11.37,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,...but I'm going to solve this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.79,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Abbacchio...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.37,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:22.04,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,There's one more mystery \N surrounding this enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:24.00,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,It's starting to come together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:25.88,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I'll solve it and kill this asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:28.22,Thoughts,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,That sense of unease \N I felt when I saw the mast... {the innuendos are just everywhere this episodio}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:29.97,Thoughts,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Earlier today...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.76,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,It's right there! \N Recall your Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:36.77,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I just solved the second mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:50.78,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Abbacchio...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:53.83,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Kill him... Buccellati!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:55.95,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,The mystery behind it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:58.21,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,The place where he's hiding...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.83,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,It's dragging you in! \N Grab my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:05.67,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.30,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,H-He's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:09.05,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:18.81,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:27.44,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,You son of a bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:30.86,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Where did you take Abbacchio?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:44.88,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,He's not in the cabin \N or the drainage pipe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:48.67,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Where are you hiding \N Abbacchio and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:57.89,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,So seein' as there's seagulls flyin' around...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:04.69,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,...we gotta be gettin' close to shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:09.11,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,I finally got you all to myself, Buccellati.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:10.69,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,You son of a{\fscx200}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:13.36,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,Oh, wait, wait, wait!
