Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:52.24,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,If you work with me, \N maybe I'll put 'em right again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:57.53,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,All you gotta do is tell me \N where Polpo's got his hidden fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:03.25,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Are you from Passione?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:06.50,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,You really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:09.13,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,...don't know nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:13.47,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,I'll fuckin' kill you, motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:16.72,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,Listen here! \N All you can say is where the money's at!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:22.52,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,Just try bullshittin' me \N with your asshole of a mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.85,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,I'll kill one of your buddies for every word!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:26.98,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,Say, "What?" and I'll kill 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.15,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,Say nothin' and I'll kill 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:31.28,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,Lie to me and I find out, \N and I'll kill 'em again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.41,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:42.33,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,Watch what you say {\i1}real{\i0} close-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:45.16,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,So lemme ask again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:49.50,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,Where's the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:56.13,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Black-tailed gulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:17:59.68,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,Huh, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:02.18,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Those aren't seagulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:03.35,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,They're black-tailed gulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:05.89,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,"How can you tell the difference?", you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:08.35,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Black-tailed gulls sound like meowing cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:12.73,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,You called them seagulls, \N but they're actually black-tailed gulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:18.82,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,I'm killin' one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:21.83,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Just try it! \N See if you don't go down with the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:28.17,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,Wh-What the fuck did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:41.22,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I didn't punch the deck \N to figure out where Abbacchio went.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:43.14,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I was putting a hole \N in the bottom of the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:44.77,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,A-A hole? {haha a-hole}{Did he just say "ona" in Japanese? Are we SURE he's not talking about his onahole?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:49.23,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Abbacchio solved the mystery\N of where you're hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:52.23,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Then he went out of his way to prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:56.28,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Now I know right where you are \N and how to expose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:57.94,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,It was Abbacchio's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:19:03.16,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,He intentionally cut his hands open \N and left a trail of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:06.33,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,A trail of blood which didn't go below deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:10.96,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,The trail ends right here on the main deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:14.50,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,So what did that tell me about \N where you dragged him off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:18.22,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I rented the yacht on the far left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:21.93,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Abbacchio realized it \N when he looked up at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:26.10,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I know right where you are, \N so if you don't want to drown...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:27.68,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,...you better show yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:40.20,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,There were two boats!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:50.79,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,Motherfucker...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:20:00.13,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,You hid by thinly covering \N this yacht with another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:06.51,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,And you attacked us by traveling \N through the thin gap between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:10.14,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,No wonder we couldn't figure it out. \N I'm actually kind of impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:12.64,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,Stay back, Buccellati!
